          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What color wavelengths does the Neck & Décolletage LED System have?",
            "text": "<p>The Neck & Décolletage LED System uses two clinically studied wavelengths of light designed to target visible signs of aging and improve the look of firmness and tone on the neck and chest: <br/></p><ul><li>Red Light (633 nm): Reaches the skin’s surface layers to help improve the appearance of firmness and smooth texture.</li><li>Near-Infrared Light (830 nm): Penetrates deeper to support the look of elasticity and even tone.</li></ul><p> Together, these wavelengths help improve the appearance of smoother-, firmer-, more even-toned skin over time — all without heat, pain, or downtime. </p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_aRwYxY": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How quickly will I see results?",
            "text": "<p>Every individual may respond differently to specific wavelengths of light, and visible improvements will depend on the skin’s condition and consistency of use.<br/><br/>Most users report seeing visible improvements within 4 to 8 weeks of consistent use. More noticeable changes may continue to appear over several months.<br/><br/>Day-to-day changes can be subtle — we recommend taking before and after photos to track your progress. Results are cumulative, so consistency is key.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_TgNixy": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is it safe for all skin types?",
            "text": "<p>Yes, this system is safe for all skin types. It is non-invasive and gentle on the skin. However, if you have specific skin conditions, we recommend consulting with a dermatologist before use.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_E8fgFz": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How often can I use the treatment?",
            "text": "<p>For best results, we recommend using the system daily.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_PgnekU": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long is one treatment?",
            "text": "<p>Just 10 minutes! A one and a half hour charge can deliver up to 7 to 8 treatments.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_FFDMmU": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use it on other areas of the body?",
            "text": "<p>While it's primarily designed for the neck and chest, some users apply it to their face or other body areas such as the back and hands. Refer to the user manual for specific usage recommendations.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_7GWRpH": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use skincare products with the system?",
            "text": "<p>For optimal results use the device on clean, bare skin. Creating a barrier between the system and your skin with unauthorized skincare products may diminish its effectiveness or potentially cause skin reactions.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_AyKUVz": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can you use this while pregnant or breastfeeding?",
            "text": "<p>Pregnant and breastfeeding individuals should exercise caution when considering any new skincare or beauty treatment. It is generally recommended to consult with a healthcare professional, before using such devices during pregnancy or while breastfeeding.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_8mgtH3": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Does the Neck & Décolletage LED System have a warranty?",
            "text": "<p>The Neck & Décolletage LED System comes with one (1) year limited warranty covering any manufacturer related problems resulting from regular use of the product. <br/><br/>To submit a claim within the warranty period, simply get in touch with our customer support team and they’ll be happy to help! </p>"
          }
        }
      },
